{"tid":241473,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大個 就越唔鍾意睇悲劇","createTime":"2017-05-13T07:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T08:15:00.000Z","uid":14383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfba8fc2203d64d07753218fda2d6704455334e4","tid":241473,"uid":14383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"以前會覺得一d故事如果剩係每一個人都稱心如意<br />\n咁會好唔真實 睇黎都冇意思<br />\n會覺得悲劇收尾嘅故事先夠真實 先夠深度<br />\n不過依家大個咗 反而掉番轉<br />\n一d主角會死 最後會失敗嘅故事會頂唔順<br />\nTbb式嘅大結局係onon99咁 不過至少冇咁虐心<br />\n之前睇clannad睇到尾二嗰集真係睇到好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係因為咁 聽人講cannon同air嘅true end 好悲都唔係好想玩<br />\n我都係想普普通通咁睇一個故事啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e77aae46bec0f3dd0dd7a2647acdc856ab71ebc","tid":241473,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n有d鍾意睇嘅戲真係會代入左個角色度<br />\n見到重要角色死我會好心噏"},{"pid":"ca0f7487224614c64e2a8398b4dbfb07ef0601c5","tid":241473,"uid":92276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得睇悲劇可以比自契機去喊岀嚟<br />\n舒服晒<br />\n平日唔會無端白事喊"},{"pid":"3de56792f0a0700419c5dd537657348fe406ef6c","tid":241473,"uid":92276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T07:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得睇悲劇可以比自己一個契機去喊岀嚟<br />\n舒服晒<br />\n平日唔會無端白事喊</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6b037939db7858c677c4429ff59f78956792bc50","tid":241473,"uid":14383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得睇悲劇可以比自己一個契機去喊岀嚟<br />\n舒服晒<br />\n平日唔會無端白事喊</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n可能我會習慣自己一個係床到喊 所以反而唔洗依d途徑去令自己釋放<br />\n只係覺得平身生活已經有壓力 仲要睇d沉重嘅故事真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d66f04b41bdaf8589b91a555fba6384e7bc840d","tid":241473,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"自己人生己經係悲劇 <br />\n唔需要再睇埋人地"},{"pid":"328e93a7ca0bd9e89bc149feb5a4e26b680f58e6","tid":241473,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:15:00.000Z","msg":"L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}